  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      38.35,
      114.03,
      278.41,
      138.53
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic SocialistRepublic of Sri Lanka as follows :\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      38.35,
      143.43,
      278.45,
      167.93
    ],
    "text": "1.This Act may be cited as the Civil Procedure Code(Amendment) Act, No. 4 of 2005.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      38.35,
      171.75,
      278.2,
      196.37
    ],
    "text": "2.Section 544 of the Civil Procedure Code is herebyamended in subsection (1) of that section as follows :\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      54.07,
      201.15,
      278.33,
      258.77
    ],
    "text": "(1)by the substitution in paragraph (e) thereof for thewords and figures \u201cwithin the meaning of theBanking Act, No. 30 of 1988,\u201d of the words andfigures \u201cwithin the meaning of the Banking Act,No. 30 of 1988; \u201d ; and",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      54.07,
      262.59,
      278.32,
      287.09
    ],
    "text": "(2)by the addition immediately after paragraph (e)thereof the following new paragraph :\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      78.79,
      290.91,
      278.5,
      348.53
    ],
    "text": "\u201c(f)any instrument relating to any monetaryinterest (other than a bearer instrument or anegotiable instrument) issued by a companyor other body of persons established in termsof any law for the time being in force,\u201d;",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      54.07,
      352.35,
      278.45,
      376.85
    ],
    "text": "(3)by the addition at the end of that subsection of thefollowing :\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      77.35,
      381.75,
      278.36,
      406.25
    ],
    "text": "\u201cFor the purposes of paragraph (f) of thissubsection \u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      98.35,
      410.19,
      278.47,
      445.73
    ],
    "text": "\u201cinstrument\u201d means a legally enforceableagreement expressing a contractual rightto the payment of money ; and",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      98.35,
      448.47,
      278.36,
      483.89
    ],
    "text": "\u201cbearer instrument\u201d means a negotiableinstrument transferable from one person toanother, upon certain conditions being met.\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      38.35,
      487.71,
      278.55,
      512.45
    ],
